---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Quote from '../components/Quote.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <span class="mono-label">index / 00</span>
  <h1>Hi, I'm Arjan.</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-dim); max-width: 60ch;">
    By trade, I'm a software engineer. By necessity, I am an innovator and designer. By passion, I am a cinephile and art aesthete.
  </p>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-dim); max-width: 60ch;">

  These distinct but meaningful aspects of my life have shaped me into who I am today. After 13 years at a Classical Educational School in Minnetonka, Minnesota, I commited to continuing my education at California Polytechnic State University in San Luis Obispo, CA. My central coast endeavors have left me passionate about education, technology, and technological ethics.
</p>
<p style="color: var(--color-text-dim); max-width: 60ch;">
  Presently, I am commited to graduating from Cal Poly with a B.S. in Software Engineering in only 3 years. Outside of the classroom, I am often at coffee shops, searching for new <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Third_place" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">third spaces</a>, playing billiards, or watching obscure films no one has heard of.
</p>
<Quote cite="— Friedrich Nietzsche">
  Never trust a thought that occurs to you indoors.
</Quote>
</BaseLayout>

